description:
&lt;p&gt;We currently have vacancies to work as Ward Coordinator Assistant&#39;s at Conquest. Duties will include general cleaning of the wards which will include buffing, wet mopping, damp dusting, toilets and disposal of waste. You will also complete the food and beverage service. The persons will need good communication skills and experience of working in a similar environment would be desirable.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Housekeepers within the hospital have a key role in our on-going fight against hospital infections &amp; make a useful contribution in the wider care team that supports a patient during their time in hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Shifts will be:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Post 1 : Wednesday - Sunday , 0700-1500 = 37.5 hpw&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Alison Brant&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Facilities Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;0300 131 4878&lt;/p&gt;
